											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The HALF-ORC shoots you a dirty look, but follows the DRIDER into the darkness, along with the other cultists. There is silence for a beat before screams start to pierce the air. There is sound of a brief battle. &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;To account for Vez being dead or alive we will rely on a Show Actor key in Node N858." />
